RTRS - Aust Infrastructure list at premium . The securities of infrastructure investor Australian Infrastructure Group made their debut on the Australian Stock Exchange on Thursday at A $ 2 . 32 , a 32 cent premium to their issue price of A $ 2 . 00 . Each security comprises one unit in the trust paid to A $ 1 . 70 stapled to one share in the company fully paid to A $ 0 . 30 . The group ' s focus is on infrastructure that investors find difficult to invest in , particularly unlisted investments . By 11 . 20 a . m . ( 0020 GMT ) , Australian Infrastructure securities were at A $ 2 . 27 with 3 . 4 million securities traded . - - Walter Watson 61 - 2 9373 1810 
